job.title: THSTI Admin Officer Recruitment 2021  Apply Online For Various  Vacancies in Faridabad
job.body:
Total Vacancies: various

Name of the Posts:

  • Administrative Officer

Description

New Central Government Jobs for Diploma holders have been published by Translational Health Science and Technology Institute for the vacancies of Administrative Officer. If you are searching for a government job in Faridabad then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Administrative Officer, from 16.04.2021, and till 15.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Faridabad and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for Gen/EWS candidates is only Rs. 500/-.

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for Administrative Officer vacancies in Faridabad, your Diploma, PG Degree, CA, ICWA must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these vacancies is 16.04.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these vacancies is 15.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 56  years old. 

THSTI Administrative Officer Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is  67700 208700/-.

How to apply for THSTI Admin Officer Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Administrative Officer. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of THSTI and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by THSTI.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
